quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,141,"Ne khandi Nyasaye yoosie balia abasuubila ne asukune ehale Abakhayi."
  3,142,"Koo, muparanga mbu mulenjilasa mumukunda kwomwikulu Nyasaye nashili okhumanya abakhalabani mwinywe nende okhumanya abokhwifwila?"
  3,143,"Ne enywe mwekombanga lifwa nimushili okhubukana nalio. Kholaano mumalile okhulilola nanyu nimuhenganga."
  3,144,"Ne Mohammad shiyali halali Omurumwa butswa, toto Abarumwa babura imbeli wuwe. Koo, nafwa nohomba niyerwa, mulafutara mukalukhe inyuma? Ne ufutara yakalukha inyuma, oyo shakholakhwo shiosishiosi Nyasaye tawe, ne Nyasaye alarunga (obulayi) bamukhupilanga orio."
  3,145,"Ne omundu shiyakhafwasa tawe halali khubuchami bwa Nyasaye, shingala yahandichilwa. Ne owenya omurungo kwokhushialo, khwitsa okhumuwa khukwo. Ne owenya omurungo kwomwikulu, khwitsa okhumuwa khukwo. Ne khularunga (obulayi) balia bakhupanga orio."
  3,146,"Ne ni Abarumwa benga ba Abasuubili abaanji bakholanga shichila Nyasaye balwaana halala ninabo, ne shibakhola oburi khukabanyoola khunjila ya Nyasaye tawe, ne shibateshelekhana tawe, ne shibatofula tawe. Ne Nyasaye yachama abefwilanga."
  3,147,"Ne shikali amakhuwa kabu halali okhuboola sa mbu, ‘’Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khuleshele ebionono biefu, nende okhubura eshichelo khwefu mumakhuwa kefu, ne tinyisia ebilenje biefu, ne okhuhabine khushile omukanda kwa Abakhayi.""
  3,148,"Mana Nyasaye nabahelesia omurungo omulayi kwokhushialo nende omurungo omulayi kwomwikulu, ne Nyasaye yachama abakholanga amalayi."